      "title": "2021 A/L exam results released",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The results of the 2021 G.C.E. Advanced Level Examination have been released.",
        "Accordingly, the results can be obtained by visiting the website of the examination department via www.doenets,lk.",
        "The total number of applicants who appeared for the 2021 A-level examination is 272,682.",
        "Of these, 171,497 applicants have qualified for university admission, the examination department said."
